post_text:
On August 14, 2017, Omega Alpha Academy had the distinct honor of having Dr. Adler (Arizona Department of Education School Improvement Instructional Coach) on campus. Dr. Adler performed various Classroom Walkthroughs, where he mentioned that OAA has made great strides in its instructional methodologies.

Dr. Adler not only brought his infinite expertise, but he also came bearing a unique gift. He brought with him a beautiful student-created collage depicting many students holding hands. The artwork is phenomenal! Omega is greatly indebted to Dr. Adler, not only for his great mentorship but also for this wonderful gift.
